sequenceDiagram
  participant Client
  participant Broker
  participant ServerA
  participant ServerB

  Client->>Broker: SQL / query options
  Broker->>Broker: parse, route, prune segments
  Broker->>ServerA: scatter sub-query
  Broker->>ServerB: scatter sub-query
  ServerA-->>Broker: partial result
  ServerB-->>Broker: partial result
  Broker->>Broker: reduce / merge / order / limit
  Broker-->>Client: BrokerResponse
